1) Copy The file 'log_failed' to /usr/bin/log_failed

	sudo cp -avr log_failed /usr/bin/log_failed

	notes : Edit the variable of environement 

2) Modify Pam Module (view with pam.d folder)

3) use the lock_screen script with crontab or Systemd service
	
	./lock_screen & 
	notes : Edit the variable of environement 

